basic.description:
{Basic Intelligence}

Increases the hero's maximum mana by 20% and grants 5 combat mana.

Combat mana is available only during combat. Some allied creatures can further increase combat mana based on their stack size if the hero has Intelligence.

advanced.description:
{Advanced Intelligence}

